      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 20:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韦丹塔出售美元债券，测试阿达尼收购印度公司后的需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/vedanta-eyes-dollar-bond-in-test-of-post-adani-india-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韦丹塔资源有限公司 (Vedanta Resources Ltd.) 为其两个月内的第三笔美元债券进行了定价，周一的交易发生在阿达尼集团创始人高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 遭美国起诉几天后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/vedanta-eyes-dollar-bond-in-test-of-post-adani-india-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 09:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
